# Implementation Plan - Subscription & Feature Access Platform

## Goal Description
Build a full-stack web application with React, Node.js, and MongoDB that manages user subscriptions and feature access. The system supports Admin, Premium, and Free users.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> Security is intentionally basic as per requirements. No real payment gateway will be implemented. Password security and MFA will be placeholders.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend (Node.js + Express)
Structure:
- `server.js`: Entry point
- `config/db.js`: MongoDB connection
- `models/`: Mongoose schemas (User, SubscriptionPlan, Feature)
- `routes/`: API routes (auth, subscriptions, admin)
- `controllers/`: Logic for routes
- `middleware/`: Auth middleware (JWT verification)

