## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- None planned as per "Keep logic simple" and "Basic UI + API only". Manual verification will be primary.

### Manual Verification
1.  **Auth**: Register a new user, Login, Check JWT token in storage, Logout.
2.  **Roles**: Login as Free user, try to access Premium content (should fail/redirect). Login as Premium, access Premium content. Login as Admin, view dashboard.
3.  **Subscription**: Click "Subscribe" on Premium plan, verify user status updates (mocked).
